OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage of the moment
OL,7,FRamal Briem was arrested at his home
OL,8,Fin Wolverhampton
OL,10,FA key member of an international
OL,11,Fpeople smuggling network involved in
OL,12,Fillegal migrant crossings to the UK
OL,13,Fhas been jailed for more than 10 years.
OL,15,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) officers
OL,16,Farrested Iraqi national Ramal Briem,
OL,17,F33, at his home address in
OL,18,FWolverhampton in July 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,FThe NCA said Briem helped to arrange
OL,7,Fthe transportation of six migrants -
OL,8,Fwhich he referred to in messages as
OL,9,F'chickens' - to Burton-on-Trent,
OL,10,FStaffordshire, in March 2024.
OL,12,FStaffordshire Police, who dealt with
OL,13,Fthe incident, arrested one person at
OL,14,Fthe time, but everyone else fled.
OL,16,FBriem admitted coming to the UK
OL,17,Fillegally by small boat in late 2020,
OL,18,Fafter which he claimed asylum and
OL,19,Ffound himself struggling financially.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,FHe said he had met a man known as
OL,7,F'Kevin', who showed an interest in how
OL,8,Fhe came to the UK as he wanted to
OL,9,Fbring some relatives over from Germany.
OL,11,FMessages on his phone showed he and
OL,12,F'Kevin', had discussed the movement of
OL,13,F'chickens' or people waiting for
OL,14,Fillegal crossings in northern France.
OL,16,FBriem is understood to have helped
OL,17,Fhundreds of migrants make such
OL,18,Fjourneys to the UK.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,F'Kevin' was one of four crime group
OL,7,Fmembers arrested by the NCA in April
OL,8,F2024 and is undergoing extradition
OL,9,Fproceedings as he is wanted in France.
OL,11,FThe other three were charged in the UK.
OL,13,FIn one exchange, published by the NCA,
OL,14,Fthe pair discuss fees for transporting
OL,15,Fmigrants after which they agree on a
OL,16,Ffee of 11 for the price of 10:
OL,18,F"'Kevin': If possible, 1 chicken costs
OL,19,F1,500 pounds. I'll give it all to you
OL,21,F"Briem: Yes 1500. Give it to me
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,F"'Kevin': Ok I'll give you the
OL,7,Fchicken. Currently I have over 30
OL,8,Fchickens in Dunkerque. I need them to
OL,9,Ffinish this time. And next time I have
OL,10,Fa new chicken I will give it to you.
OL,12,F"Briem: Ok. Next time I need all your
OL,13,Fchicken."
OL,15,FBriem had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fa charge of conspiracy to assist
OL,17,Funlawful immigration at Wolverhampton
OL,18,FCrown Court in October 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774541483
OL,3,CPeople smuggler who referred to
OL,4,Cmigrants as 'chickens' jailed
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 10 years and two
OL,7,Fmonths imprisonment at Worcester Crown
OL,8,FCourt today (26 March).
OL,10,FNCA branch commander Saju Sasikumar
OL,11,Fsaid "The language Ramal Briem used to
OL,12,Fdescribe people illustrates his
OL,13,Fcomplete disregard for human life.
OL,15,F"To him, migrants were nothing more
OL,16,Fthan a commodity to trade in,
OL,17,Fregardless of the severe risks they
OL,18,Fwere taking during these dangerous
OL,19,Fjourneys, all for his own financial
OL,20,Fbenefit."
OL,26,@sD@FOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
